    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……ついにクラフモ監督とのオンライン会議です\nき、き、緊張が……！",
      "startTime": 6.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "送ったアイデアを見た先方の反応は良かったんだし\nそこまで緊張しなくてもいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 12.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "心の準備はもちろんしてきているんですけど\nやっぱり本人にお会いすると思うと……",
      "startTime": 19.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "まず自分の伝えたいことをしっかり伝えるようにしよう\n大丈夫だ。何かあっても俺がフォローするから",
      "startTime": 27.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。……おかげで落ち着きました\n自分の口で伝えるべきことをしっかり伝えます！",
      "startTime": 36.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "その意気だ。……っと、そろそろ会議が始まるぞ\n頑張ろうな、千紗",
      "startTime": 45.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　すぅー……ふぅー……よし\n決めてきた挨拶をちゃんと言わなきゃ",
      "startTime": 52.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "本日はお時間を頂戴しまして誠にありがとうございます\nどうぞよろしくお願いします",
      "startTime": 60.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "ぶ……ブエナス・タルデス！\nセニョール、クラフモ……",
      "startTime": 64.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗！？　ど、どうしたんだ急に！？\nそもそもそれは何語だ！？",
      "startTime": 69.8333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "クラフモ監督はスペインの方ですので\nスペイン語をちょっと勉強してきたんです",
      "startTime": 75.0666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "その努力は素晴らしいが、落ち着いてくれ\n向こうにはちゃんと通訳さんがいるから……！",
      "startTime": 80.4666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃあっ！？　ほ、本当だ\nすみません、私勘違いしちゃってて",
      "startTime": 85.699995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええと、白石はクラフモ監督とお話しするために\nスペイン語を勉強していたんです",
      "startTime": 94.6333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（これがフォローになるかは分からないが）\n（失礼のないようにしておかないとな）",
      "startTime": 99.3666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　健気で可愛い子だね、って……\nあ、ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 107.2333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（どうやら千紗の健気な姿勢が監督に）\n（気に入ってもらえたようだ）",
      "startTime": 112.7999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "では、私が考えたアイデアについて説明しますね\n事前にお送りした資料をご覧下さい",
      "startTime": 119.7666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後",
      "startTime": 123.7333318075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "今日は付き合ってくれてありがとうございます\n楽しみ過ぎて、早起きしちゃいました",
      "startTime": 129.4999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "無理もない。制作中のお化け屋敷に入れる機会なんて\nそうそうないからな",
      "startTime": 137.0295654989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　監修のためではありますけど\nしっかりと隅々まで確認させてもらおうと思います！",
      "startTime": 141.9333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "会議で出たアイデアを参考に作ってくれたみたいですが\nどんな感じになってるんでしょうか",
      "startTime": 150.5999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "映画の世界観を再現するためにいろいろと意見を\nお伝えしたので、凄く楽しみです",
      "startTime": 157.2333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "クラフモ監督も千紗の出したアイデアを\n気に入ってくれていたしな",
      "startTime": 162.6666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "少し攻めた提案内容かもしれないと\n思っていたので、安心しました",
      "startTime": 167.5999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、いちお客さんとして楽しみつつ\nいろいろと確認していきましょう",
      "startTime": 174.4999949138,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_horror-01.m4a",
